  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our Discord</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525490/extras/097465cc909f6a9e6c06d1361a70d65b.avif?t=1728291823\" width=616 height=196 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>A unique fusion of farming and slapstick combat, Harvest Havoc is a chaotic online PvP party game for 2-6 players. Grow, harvest, (steal) and sell your crops to win! Fight with your fists or grow some weapons to mess with your friends and aid your crop-stealing mischief. Gather your friends, bring out your inner gremlin and compete to become the ultimate farmer-warrior!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer for 6</h2>Best played with friends, family or co-workers, play with up to 5 other farmer-warriors in online multiplayer<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grow, Harvest, Sell!</h2>Find the seed packets scattered around the map and plant it to start your farming spree. Be the one to earn the most money. But watch out: farmers might have their eyes on your precious crops.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525490/extras/9c1cafcd4ef9befa15215b79d6501d87.poster.avif?t=1728291823\" width=512 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525490/extras/9c1cafcd4ef9befa15215b79d6501d87.webm?t=1728291823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525490/extras/9c1cafcd4ef9befa15215b79d6501d87.mp4?t=1728291823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Steal & Sabotage!</h2>Wanna mess around with your friends? Use your fists or grow some weapons to smack them around and steal their crops for yourself!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525490/extras/6bbe48236cdb3612273382e18a5aaf1e.poster.avif?t=1728291823\" width=530 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525490/extras/6bbe48236cdb3612273382e18a5aaf1e.webm?t=1728291823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525490/extras/6bbe48236cdb3612273382e18a5aaf1e.mp4?t=1728291823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Teams VS Free-for-all</h2>Want to work together? Or is it every farmer for themselves? Choose how you want to play.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525490/extras/d6b96ca5984522b5a020da9205263da7.poster.avif?t=1728291823\" width=530 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525490/extras/d6b96ca5984522b5a020da9205263da7.webm?t=1728291823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525490/extras/d6b96ca5984522b5a020da9205263da7.mp4?t=1728291823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Character Selection</h2>Choose your wacky character from a selection of 5 animal costumes and 8 colours.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525490/extras/3c18bddd2e26f79ad9a8a23a3bbda951.poster.avif?t=1728291823\" width=528 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525490/extras/3c18bddd2e26f79ad9a8a23a3bbda951.webm?t=1728291823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525490/extras/3c18bddd2e26f79ad9a8a23a3bbda951.mp4?t=1728291823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >5 Thematic Maps & 3 Game Modes</h2>Play in a variety of \"farms\" with different ways to play and navigate each map. If it feels too slow for you or you want more bare-knuckle brawling, try out the different game modes!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525490/extras/051b8d87aa57d87e98889e027e5c8bc9.poster.avif?t=1728291823\" width=530 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525490/extras/051b8d87aa57d87e98889e027e5c8bc9.webm?t=1728291823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525490/extras/051b8d87aa57d87e98889e027e5c8bc9.mp4?t=1728291823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
